Title: Un Papá Pirata
Writer: Yibran Asuad, Anton Goenechea, Pedro 'Zulu' González, Humberto Hinojosa Ozcariz
Actors: Miguel Rodarte, Juan Pablo Medina, Luis de La Rosa, Natasha Dupeyrón
Plot: Ian discovers that André, a former soap opera star and current alcoholic is his real father. Ian decides to go work at his ruined mascot business where he finds a place populated by extravagant people and discovers the meaning of fatherhood.
